metadata.author: Jake Harris
metadata.description: Big ideas for little ears. Story Shed is a storytelling podcast for children of all ages and their parents. Created by former Primary School teacher Jake Harris as a way of inspiring families to enjoy stories with a heart. All the stories on Story Shed are original stories written by Jake. Also perfect a teaching resource, ideal for assemblies.
